#!/bin/bash

cat << 'EOF'
VIM HOTKEYS (leader = \)

ERGONOMICS
───────────────────────────────────
Exit insert mode    jj
Command mode        ;  (not :)
Paste mode toggle   F2  (use before Cmd+V)
Paste from system   \p  (normal mode)

NAVIGATION
───────────────────────────────────
Go to definition    gd
References          gr
Type definition     gy
Implementation      gi
Hover docs          K
Jump back           Ctrl+o
Jump forward        Ctrl+i

FILES & SEARCH
───────────────────────────────────
Fuzzy find files    Ctrl+p
Buffers             \b
Ripgrep search      \rg
File tree toggle    \n
Find file in tree   \f

SPLITS & TABS (from fzf/NERDTree)
───────────────────────────────────
Vertical split      Ctrl+v / v
Horizontal split    Ctrl+s / s
New tab             Ctrl+t / t

WINDOWS
───────────────────────────────────
Move left           Ctrl+w h
Move down           Ctrl+w j
Move up             Ctrl+w k
Move right          Ctrl+w l
Swap windows        Ctrl+w x
Equalize size       Ctrl+w =
Next tab            gt
Previous tab        gT

CODE
───────────────────────────────────
Rename symbol       \rn
Outline             \o
Undo tree           \u
Comment line        gcc
Comment selection   gc (visual mode)
Colorscheme picker  ;Colors

SESSIONS
───────────────────────────────────
Save session        \ss
Restore session     \sr
EOF
